    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Our Story</h1>
                <p>25+ Years of Digital Transformation</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Timeline Section -->
    <section class="timeline-section">
        <div class="timeline-container">
            <div class="timeline">
                <!-- 1997 - X-Tech Founded -->
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">1997</div>
                        <h3>Humble Beginnings, Enduring Vision</h3>
                        <p>Our journey began when our founder was in college in Oklahoma City, Oklahoma in the late 90's. What started as part-time work helping local people and small businesses find the right technology solutions quickly revealed a deeper calling: the realization that successful technology adoption isn't just about selecting the right tools—it's about understanding the human side of change.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Y2K Tech Milestone -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">1999-2000</div>
                        <h3>Y2K: Tech Industry Wake-Up Call</h3>
                        <p>The millennium bug shifted how businesses viewed technology strategy. Organizations worldwide scrambled to ensure systems could handle the year 2000 transition, proving the critical importance of legacy system management—a cornerstone of our practice today.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">📅 Industry Milestone</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2000s - Decades of Evolution -->
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2000s</div>
                        <h3>Decades of Digital Evolution</h3>
                        <p>For over 25 years, we've been in the trenches of business transformation, watching technologies evolve from early business computing to today's AI-powered solutions. This deep historical perspective gives us something many consultants lack: we've seen what works, what doesn't, and why.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Windows XP Release -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2001</div>
                        <h3>Windows XP Revolutionizes Computing</h3>
                        <p>Windows XP became the gold standard for enterprise computing, driving widespread business PC adoption. Its stability and ease of use fundamentally changed how SMBs approached technology infrastructure.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">💻 Technology Shift</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2007 - SSD Era -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2007</div>
                        <h3>SSD Revolution Begins</h3>
                        <p>Solid-state drives emerged, fundamentally changing storage performance and reliability. This technology shift enabled faster, more dependable computing and became central to modern infrastructure strategies we recommend today.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">⚡ Hardware Evolution</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2009 - Bitcoin -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2009</div>
                        <h3>Bitcoin & Blockchain Emerge</h3>
                        <p>Bitcoin introduced blockchain technology to the world, sparking a revolution in distributed systems, security, and data integrity. This innovation continues to reshape how we think about trust and transactions in business.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">🔗 Paradigm Shift</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Cloud Computing -->
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2010s</div>
                        <h3>The Cloud Transforms Business</h3>
                        <p>Cloud computing matured into a mainstream business necessity. As organizations migrated from on-premise infrastructure, we were there helping businesses navigate the transition, manage hybrid environments, and unlock the potential of cloud-first strategies.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- ChatGPT Release -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2022</div>
                        <h3>ChatGPT Launches the AI Era</h3>
                        <p>OpenAI's ChatGPT democratized large language models, making AI accessible to businesses of all sizes. This moment marked the beginning of enterprise AI adoption and fundamentally changed what's possible with technology transformation.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">🤖 AI Breakthrough</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Today -->
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">Today</div>
                        <h3>The Cross-Industry Advantage</h3>
                        <p>Unlike consultants who specialize in specific industries or technologies, we deliberately maintain a broad perspective. This cross-pollination approach allows us to bring innovative solutions from manufacturing to healthcare, from retail insights to professional services, and from startup agility to enterprise stability.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Future -->
                <div class="timeline-item tech-milestone">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">Future</div>
                        <h3>Looking Forward: AI-Driven Transformation</h3>
                        <p>We continue to evolve alongside our clients and the technology landscape. We're developing custom solutions that will allow us to extend our proven methodologies to even more small businesses, leveraging AI and cloud technologies to make enterprise-level transformation accessible and economical for companies of all sizes.</p>
                        <span class="tech-label">🚀 Next Frontier</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

